text: Game Paisa Ladki is a Bollywood film released on 21 September 2018 starring Zakir Hussain, Sitaram Panchal, Ashraful Haque (actor) and Sezal Sharma. Zakir Hussain plays the role of a psycho lover. Singer Kunal Ganjawala and Jubin Nautiyal recorded a song for the film. ==References== Category:Hindi-language films Category:2018 films Category:Indian films Category:2010s Hindi-language films
